        ''' <param name="data">Õâ¸öµÄË³ÐòÓëÊýÄ¿±ØÐëÒªÓë<see cref="_CodeMappings"></see>»òÕß<see cref="_originals"></see>ÏàÒ»ÖÂ</param>
        ''' <returns></returns>
